#: aperisolve/templates/index.html:2
msgid "Aperi'Solve - Online Image Steganography Analyzer"
msgstr "Aperi'Solve - 在线图片隐写分析工具"

#: aperisolve/templates/index.html:3
msgid ""
"Free online steganography analysis: layer/bit-plane extraction plus "
"zsteg, steghide, binwalk, exiftool, foremost, outguess and more on PNG, "
"JPG, GIF, BMP, TIFF and WebP images."
msgstr ""
"免费在线隐写分析：图层与位平面提取，以及 zsteg、steghide、binwalk、exiftool、foremost、outguess "
"等工具，支持 PNG、JPG、GIF、BMP、TIFF 和 WebP 图片。"

#: aperisolve/templates/index.html:28
msgid "What is this?"
msgstr "这是什么？"

#: aperisolve/templates/index.html:30
msgid ""
"Aperi'Solve is an online platform which performs layer analysis on "
"images.\n"
"      The platform also uses zsteg, steghide, outguess, exiftool, "
"binwalk, foremost and strings\n"
"      for deeper steganography analysis. Supports: PNG, JPG, GIF, BMP, "
"JPEG, JFIF, JPE, TIFF..."
msgstr ""
"Aperi'Solve 是一个对图片进行图层分析的在线平台。平台还使用 "
"zsteg、steghide、outguess、exiftool、binwalk、foremost 和 strings "
"进行更深入的隐写分析。支持：PNG、JPG、GIF、BMP、JPEG、JFIF、JPE、TIFF..."

